2000-05-21  Dave Love  <fx@gnu.org>

	* edmacro.el (edmacro-parse-keys): Return vector if any elements
	are invalid characters.

	* international/mule-util.el (detect-coding-with-priority): Use
	mapc.  Remove redundant lambda.

