	* msb.el (msb--choose-file-menu): Use `(apply #'list ...)'
	instead of copy-list which is a function from CL.
	(msb--choose-menu, msb--mode-menu-cond)
	(msb--create-buffer-menu-2): Use dolist instead of mapc.
